The '''Clan Vos''' was a [[Kiffar/Legends|Kiffar]] family. For a time they were the rulers of the [[Planet/Legends|planets]] [[Kiffu/Legends|Kiffu]] and [[Kiffex/Legends|Kiffex]]. The Clan's insignia was a gold five-point star enclosed by a gold circle, the same symbol used by the [[Kiffu Guardians]]<ref name="JvS">[[Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force (real-life book)|''Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force'']]</ref>. Facial markings that traditionally represented the Vos clan included vertical bars of yellow/off-white over the middle third of the face and smaller horizontal bars across the bridge of the nose and cheeks.

